  "texts": [
    "Define ζ(x):= q(x)-p(x) p(x), ∀x ∈ Ω.",
    "Then D KL (p∥q) = Ω p(x) log p(x) q(x) dx = -Ω p(x) log(1 + ζ(x)) dx.",
    "Define two Borel sets as follows, A:= {x|ζ(x) > 1} = {x|q(x) > 2p(x)}, B:= {x|ζ(x) ≤ 1} = {x|q(x) ≤ 2p(x)}.",
    "We obtain that for x ∈ A, 1 + ζ(x) ≤ e αζ(x) where α = log 2; for x ∈ B, 1 + ζ(x) ≤ e ζ(x)-βζ(x) 2 where β = 1 -log 2.",
    "Note that p and q are two probabilities density on Ω, that isΩ p(x)ζ(x) dx = Ω (q(x) -p(x)) dx = 0, which implies that A p(x)ζ(x) dx = -B p(x)ζ(x) dx."
